      1          /**
      2           *  @file       
      3           *
      4           *    @brief    This module implements the standard Flash API (Application Programming Interface)
      5           *              for STM32F0x
      6           *    @details  This modules provides the interface to application in order to write or
      7           *              format the Flash of STM32G0x.
      8           *              Note -  1. Controller supports only 8 byte addressed write. If the application tries to write on odd address
      9           *                         gives error.
     10           *                      2. Controller supports only 8 byte write. Application can write 1 byte were the next adjacent byte
     11           *                         is written with 0xff(because the controller support word writing)
     12           *                      3. The software design supports for odd size write.
     13           *                         The next adjacent byte is written with 0xff(because the controller support word writing)
     14           *                      4. Before writing data on the memory the flash memory should have erase value(0xff).
     15           *                      5. Fast programming is performed writing 256 bytes
     16           *
     17           *  @section    Applicable_Documents
     18           *                  List here all the applicable documents if needed. <tr>
     19           *
     20           *  $Header: $
     21           *
     22           *  @copyright  Copyright 2021-$Date$. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     23           */
